label.string: Guess the WORDLE in six tries. Each guess must be a valid five-letter word. Hit "return" to submit. After each guess, the color of the tiles will change to show how close your guess was.
GREEN means the guessed letter is in the word and in the correct spot. YELLOW means the letter is in the word but in the wrong spot. GRAY means the letter is not in the word in any spot
